### StorageOperationStoringPolicy API Tests

### Get all storage operation storing policies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get storage operation storing policy by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get storage operation storing policy by StorageOperationId
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy/by-storage-operation/{{storageOperationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create a new storage operation storing policy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storageOperationId": "{{storageOperationId}}",
  "name": "Default Policy",
  "transitionInDays": 90,
  "expirationInDays": null
}

###

### Create a policy with expiration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "storageOperationId": "{{storageOperationId}}",
  "name": "Short Term Policy",
  "transitionInDays": 30,
  "expirationInDays": 365
}

###

### Update an existing storage operation storing policy
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "{{policyId}}",
  "storageOperationId": "{{storageOperationId}}",
  "name": "Updated Policy",
  "transitionInDays": 60,
  "expirationInDays": 180
}

###

### Delete a storage operation storing policy
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/StorageOperationStoringPolicy/{{policyId}}
Content-Type: application/json

